videos.headline: Trask finds Pitts for 1st Gator TD of day
videos.description: Kyle Trask finds Kyle Pitts for a 19-yard touchdown in Trask's first-ever start as a Florida Gator.

videos.headline: Perine fights for short TD

videos.headline: Florida's Burney flies for impressive interception

videos.headline: Trask powers Gators past Vols in first career start
videos.description: Kyle Trask throws for 293 yards and two touchdowns as the Gators power past conference foe Tennessee 34-3.
